# [Feature]  ANOM-FEAT-XXX
# [Module]   CanAnomalyDetectionLogic / CanSignal / OemCustomization / AuditLog / ...
# [Decision] DR-YYYY-MMDD-NN
# [Reason]   (変更の理由・目的)
# [Impact]   (影響範囲: parameter range / approval flow / IF / ...)
# [IF]       changed / unchanged
# [DOC]      pending / not_required / updated
#
# --- 上記コメントを消去して実際のコミットメッセージを書いてください ---
#
# 例:
#   feat(CanSignal): add CommonalityStatus and traceability fields
#
#   [Feature]  ANOM-FEAT-017
#   [Module]   CanSignal
#   [Decision] DR-2026-0504-01
#   [Reason]   資産共通化分類の判断保留（Unknown）を期限付きで管理するため
#   [Impact]   CanSignal UpdateAsync, EF migration
#   [IF]       unchanged
#   [DOC]      pending
